# Commerce Domain

Owns: catalog, personalization, gift box, cart, checkout, orders, inventory, promotions, commerce admin.

Does not own: editorial publish gates, creator bidding.

## Invariants

- Personalization on one line must not mutate another
- Coupons do not stack unless configured
- Legal order state transitions only
- Cancel/fail payment releases inventory reservations
- Server recomputes prices — never trust client totals
- Guest→user cart merge must be deterministic

Build Your Box UX: show **Remaining Budget** on mobile summary (not cart total) when in builder.
